        <div class="container-std custom-content">
          <h2 class="h2 mb-5">VIDEO</h2>

          <strong class="font-bold">THE PROJECT</strong>
          <p>Native Bionics face the challenge of creating awareness for their product. Parents, their target audience did not find reasons to purchase the product. Nor did Native Bionics have funds to spend on advertising. To be able to market the product I was asked to create a video which would be shared on Social Media</p>
          
          <strong class="font-bold">MY ROLE</strong>
          <p>I was solely responsible for the entire project, which involved idea, story, storyboard, location scouting, directing, filming (with an SLR) and editing of the video</p>
          
          <strong class="font-bold">THE RESULT</strong>
          <p>The outcome became an informative and convincing story highlighting the point that parents want the best for their children</p>
          
          <p>NOTE: The voice-over is not final</p>
        </div>

        
