        <div class="container-std custom-content">
            <h2 class="mb-5">LOGO / PACKAGE</h2>
            <strong class="font-bold">THE PROJECT</strong>
            <p>The purpose was to create a product identity for Surf which fitted in conjunction with the brand logo as well as stand alone.</p>

            <strong class="font-bold">MY ROLE</strong>
            <p>I was responsible for ideas, sketches and final artwork.</p>

            <strong class="font-bold">THE RESULT</strong>
            <p>A visual identity which gives a soft and playful feeling yet simplistic, which fitted well with the brand logo. The logo was used for all marketing purposes and when I created the packaging. It was also applied to the labels on the product itself. </p>
        </div>

